summary:
Contract Renounced - This action removes the ability for the team to make changes to the contract, ensuring decentralization and providing assurance to investors that the token's protocol is immutable and secure.

 Contract Audited - This audit ensures the integrity, security, and functionality of the contract, providing peace of mind to investors regarding the safety of their transactions and investments.

 Fair Allocations - This principle ensures that all participants have a reasonable opportunity to obtain tokens without any unfair advantages, promoting inclusivity and transparency within the community.
